terms.medium_def:
A man living before Israel's Monarchy, first mentioned at Rut.1.2; 
only referred to as Chilion (כִּלְיוֹן); 
son of Elimelech and Naomi; 
a brother of Mahlon; 
husband of Orpah. § an Ephraimite and son of Elimelech by Naomi and the deceased husband of Ruth (or maybe deceased husband of Orpah)
